(see https://derekkedziora.com/blog/digital-tidying-the-links)

- same with numbered lists
(see https://derekkedziora.com/blog/western-consensus-thinking)

- maybe make aside class 
(see https://derekkedziora.com/blog/corona-western-consensus-thinking)

- quotes should have slightly different font size
(see https://derekkedziora.com/blog/imperialism-of-chomsky)

- code blocks styling and background

- modified markdown style guide

